VS Code extension tutorial flow:
When the topic involves installing and using a VS Code extension, structure the
sections to follow this exact user journey:
1. Open VS Code → click Extensions icon → search → Install the extension
2. Open the Chat panel → see the new agents available to pick from
3. Use @task-researcher to research a simple task (e.g., explore titanic.csv)
4. Review the research output (markdown files in the explorer)
5. Use @task-planner to plan the implementation → Use @implementer to code it

